

	EDUC-K 780  SEMINAR IN SPECIAL EDUCATION (3 CR)
              10969          02:30P-05:15P   T      ED 2280   Butera G                 10    8    0
                 TOPIC : Preparing Professionals for Inclusive Classrooms
                 Above class open to Doctoral and  Advanced Master's students
                 K780 : In this seminar we will examine research and policy
                 about teachers and teacher preparation in both general and
                 special education. We will review research and practices
                 about preservice and I service teacher development. Finally
                 we will consider what teachers know and need to know to enact
                 and support inclusive educational practices.
        
